---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Transparent Pricing"
  description="BharatDCIM pricing starts at ₹500/rack/month—85% below global DCIM vendors. No hidden fees, transparent per-rack pricing for Indian data centers."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="section-label">Pricing</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Simple, Transparent<br />
          <span class="text-[--color-accent]">Per-Rack Pricing</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          85% below global DCIM vendors. No surprise fees.
          Pay only for the racks you manage.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Cards -->
  <section class="section pt-0">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Starter -->
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Starter</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-6">For small deployments</p>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[--color-primary] mb-2">
            ₹500
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">per rack / month</p>

          <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-6">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">Best for 10-50 racks</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Asset tracking & management
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Rack visualization
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Tenant management
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Basic billing (manual entry)
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Email support
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary w-full mt-8 justify-center">Get Started</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Professional -->
        <div class="card border-[--color-accent] border-2 relative scale-105">
          <span class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-[--color-accent] text-white text-sm px-4 py-1 rounded-full font-medium">Most Popular</span>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Professional</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-6">For growing operators</p>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[--color-primary] mb-2">
            ₹800
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">per rack / month</p>

          <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-6">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">Best for 50-200 racks</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Everything in Starter
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                <strong>ToD billing engine</strong>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Power monitoring integration
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Environmental monitoring
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                GST-compliant invoicing
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                SLA tracking & reporting
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Tenant self-service portal
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Priority support
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary w-full mt-8 justify-center">Get Started</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Enterprise -->
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Enterprise</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-6">For large operators</p>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[--color-primary] mb-2">
            ₹1,200
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">per rack / month</p>

          <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-6">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">Best for 200+ racks</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Everything in Professional
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Multi-site management
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                API access & integrations
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                White-labeled tenant portal
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Advanced analytics
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Custom integrations
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                Dedicated account manager
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[--color-accent]">✓</span>
                SLA guarantee
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary w-full mt-8 justify-center">Contact Sales</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Discounts -->
      <div class="mt-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">Volume Discounts</h3>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[--color-primary]">17%</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Annual billing discount</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[--color-primary]">10%</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">500+ racks discount</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[--color-primary]">15%</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">1000+ racks discount</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comparison -->
  <section class="section bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="section-label">Value</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          85% Below<br />
          <span class="accent">Global DCIM Pricing</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <thead class="bg-[--color-primary] text-white">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold">Vendor</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold">Pricing Model</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold">100-Rack Cost</th>
              <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold">India ToD Support</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium">Nlyte</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4">$1,000/rack + connectors</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4">$100,000+</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-red-500">No</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium">Sunbird</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4">$490-$700/rack</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4">$49,000-$70,000</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-red-500">No</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium">Device42</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4">$1,449-$9,999/year</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4">~$5,000/year</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-red-500">No</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-[--color-primary]/5">
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-bold text-[--color-primary]">BharatDCIM</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4">₹800/rack/month</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 font-bold">₹9.6L/year (~$11,500)</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-green-600 font-medium">Yes - Native</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="section-label">FAQ</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          Common<br />
          <span class="accent">Questions</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What counts as a "rack"?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Any rack, cage, or cabinet that you manage in the system. Partially filled racks count the same as full racks. Private suites are counted by the number of rack positions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Are there any setup fees?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">No setup fees for Starter and Professional plans. Enterprise deployments may include optional professional services for custom integrations and data migration.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I start with a pilot?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes! We offer pilot programs for qualified operators. Contact us to discuss a 3-month pilot at reduced pricing to validate ROI before full deployment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What's included in support?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">All plans include email support. Professional adds priority response times. Enterprise includes a dedicated account manager and phone support.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you offer GST invoicing?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, all invoices are GST-compliant with proper SAC codes. We're registered in India and issue invoices in INR.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section bg-[--color-primary] text-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
          Ready to Get Started?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10">
          Schedule a demo to see BharatDCIM in action and discuss your specific requirements.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-light text-lg px-8 py-4">Schedule Demo</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
